from geb gordon bank subject re mississippus river water and catfish safe in article dfield infospunj dan field write i be invite to spend a couple week thi summer raft down the mississippus my journey partner want to live off of river water and catfish along the route should i have any concern about pollution or health risk in do thi you have to purify the river water first i not sure how practical that be with the mississippus you better check with health agency along the way to see if there be toxic chemical in the river if it be just microorganism those can be filter or kill but you may need activate charcoal or other mean to purify from chemical better be same than sorry obviously drink the river without process it be likely to make you sick from bacterium and parasite gordon bank skepticism be the chastity of the intellect and geb it be shameful to surrender it too soon 